 <H1>Software Developmentï¿½ via the Web</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>Advantages of leveraging the Web for software development:
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Geographic distribution: Software development artifacts can be accessed via the network
<LI>Use the browser: Ubiquitous browsers can easily view development artifacts
<LI>Leverage existing infrastructure: Many tools already use the Web
<LI>Builds on open standards: Web standards are open, yielding many suppliers, often open source, for components.  Keeps infrastructure costs low.</UL></UL></P>
